Class LegendEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.fmap.mapcontext.events.FMapEvent
      • org.gvsig.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.legend.events.LegendEvent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassificationLegendEvent, LabelLegendEvent, LegendChangedEvent

    public class LegendEvent
extends FMapEvent

    LegendEvent represents an event produced at a legend in a layer.
